DataElement.preferredDefinition: Development is the act, or process, of natural progression in physical and psychological maturation from a previous, lower, or embryonic stage to a later, more complex, or adult stage.:Any distinct time period in a sequence of events._An indicator that can be set or unset in order to signal whether a particular condition is true.:Capable of being estimated or expressed with numeric values._Generic value domain for a primitive java datatype that is a Boolean value (true or false).
